text: The 2016 Sealect Tuna Women's Volleyball Championship () officially known as the 2016 Annual H.R.H. Princess Maha Chakri Sirindhorn's Cup Volleyball Tournament was a national volleyball competition. It was organized by the Thailand Volleyball Association or the TVA.
